157
00:08:34,588 --> 00:08:35,673
Tidak.

158
00:08:36,458 --> 00:08:41,742
Aku hanya ingat sedikit.

159
00:08:42,238 --> 00:08:46,883
Sejak kapan kamu mulai mengingat setiap hal kecil?

160
00:08:47,308 --> 00:08:50,683
